{"tid":264884,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【哪有錢！】調查：逾六成年青人入不敷支 三成人欠債","createTime":"2017-05-31T08:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T14:02:54.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d4b6d72b7853e6fe40345d63091a09a7d76c741","tid":264884,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170531/large/1496216768_13bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170531%2Flarge%2F1496216768_13bb.jpg&h=410241f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投資者教育中心於2017年4月訪問了500位年齡介乎18至29歲的在職成年人，62%人入不敷支，31%受訪者背負債務，平均欠款3.7萬元，近四成受訪者並未訂立財務目標，其餘大部分人僅着眼於短期目標，例如計劃旅行，忽視長遠規劃；在職年輕人承認對投資所知甚少。<br />\n<br />\n受訪者當中有86%面臨一項或多項個人財務挑戰，他們最常見的憂慮分別包括缺乏投資知識（51%）、置業困難（49%）和儲蓄不足（42%），有11%的受訪者表示因債務感到壓力。大部分年輕人（88%）擁有信用卡，但約五分之一未能每月全數還款，平均信用卡債務達 2萬元。有8%承認完全沒有儲蓄習慣。<br />\n<br />\n逾三分之一受訪者表示平均每份工作僅維持一年或更短時間，更有44%的受訪者曾裸辭。<br />\n<br />\n過去一年，有32%的在職年輕人並未參與任何投資活動，有投資的則大多傾向短視近利，對投資回報抱有不切實際的期望。86%的受訪者承認對金融投資產品所知甚少或一無所知。有投資的受訪者方面，69%股票投資者採取少於一年的短線投資期，少於半數（43%）有訂立止蝕策略。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56764928&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56764928%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170531&d=e9O9amzqvGH8pRtNz3tTughMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=af8c9723\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56764928%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170531&h=68b48154\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56764928&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170531</a>"},{"pid":"6210fa64419edfa2fac350f54a465b707c6ae574","tid":264884,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:06:01.000Z","msg":"我諗起借錢廣告：<br />\n<br />\n現場睇演唱會勁正<br />\n渡蜜月<br />\n買相機影多D靚相<br />\n同一個款，兩隻顏色嘅長裙，買哂佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e253035c9e0ad1844bb2b8523c7b29d7ff915e","tid":264884,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:08:37.000Z","msg":"無可能"},{"pid":"b2f27551b129c9c8c2e6647a6a9b969c657f4161","tid":264884,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"我係咪生活喺平行世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc325aa21fbacacccdbd4f306c19b9c5c61a1fe","tid":264884,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:13:50.000Z","msg":"我啲朋友最多月月清糧，但都月月清卡數，真係有報導咁多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37d1ba1027b65f4300c0dd260d5bc3af30ac355","tid":264884,"uid":104591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:14:29.000Z","msg":"逾8成青年 年年去旅行"},{"pid":"67ece826ef464435363b2c7ea75a58ff774b4d94","tid":264884,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:15:34.000Z","msg":"每個月要找卡數當欠債？"},{"pid":"a0eba5e8d82f893b9a888242f4b1cff0e82d490e","tid":264884,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗起借錢廣告：<br />\n<br />\n現場睇演唱會勁正<br />\n渡蜜月<br />\n買相機影多D靚相<br />\n同一個款，兩隻顏色嘅長裙，買哂佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲廣告其實好仆街，講到借咗唔洗還咁"},{"pid":"a37ea1c883ead945066ba2127e68f05187866b04","tid":264884,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:18:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2334b4ebb98ba3514b7001bbcc5317872fb72e6","tid":264884,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:57:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係